{"type":"answer","id":120307,"parentType":"question","parentId":14563,"uid":25704,"contents":"说三点：<br>\n<br>\n1 穆斯林不可强迫非穆斯林守教规，因此穆斯林尊重非穆斯林的饮食自由。<br>\n“对於宗教，绝无强迫；因为正邪确已分明了。”（2：256）<br>\n<br>\n2 国航可自由选餐，若坐上清真食品的航班，只需要在登机前勾选餐点即可。<br>\n<a href=\"http://www.airchina.com.cn/cn/info/flight-experience/meals/special-meals/religion/special_r3_2.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.airchina.com.cn/cn/info/flight-experience/meals/special-meals/religion/special_r3_2.shtml<br>\n</a><br>\n3 国航清真餐与一般餐没有太大分别<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/71foB61.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/71foB61.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/71foB61.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-01-03","agreeCount":2,"discussionCount":0}